Description: 格式化正则内容输出
        ===============
        
        $0、$1、$2 分别对应 match中的g0、g1、g2、g3
        
        multi是否为多重匹配，是则返回所有结果，否则返回首匹配
        
        
        
            >>> data = '12m34kjdg8946o'
            >>> pn = '(\d)([a-z])'
            >>> fm = '$1,$2'
            >>> result = extract(pn, data, fm)
            >>> result
            '2,m'
            >>> result = extract(pn, data, fm, multi= True)
            >>> result
            ['2,m', '4,k', '6,o']
            
Platform: any
